name: Chapter does not apply to active duty armed forces, national guard, armed forces reserve, or Police Activities League
text: This chapter shall not apply to any mixed martial arts contest held as a recreational activity by active duty armed forces, armed forces reserve, or national guard personnel, or the Police Activities League, when the contest is held under the supervision of a recreational officer of the active duty armed forces, armed forces reserve, national guard, or a Police Activities League staff member. [L 2007, c 279, pt of §1]
